    <section class="flexibleblocks-block __smlmargin">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row offset-xl-1">
                <div class="col-12 col-xl-11">
                    <div class="imagetext __animate ">
                            <div class="imagetext-image">
                                <img src="/media/e2heuikx/dsc9488-ansawddgwefan.jpg?anchor=center&amp;mode=crop&amp;width=650&amp;height=430&amp;rnd=132711701374000000" alt="image of five people sitting by a castle" data-object-fit="cover">
                            </div>
                        <div class="imagetext-body">
                            <div class="usercontent">
                                <p>The <a href="/about-us/welsh-language-commissioners-leadership-team" title="Whose on the Welsh Language Commissioner's management team?">Commissioner</a> promotes and facilitates opportunities to use the Welsh language.</p>
<p>This includes ensuring that you are able to receive services in Welsh from <a href="/your-rights/what-organisations-have-to-do" title="What do organisations have to do?">public organisations</a> in Wales. </p>
<p>From time-to-time things can go wrong. It is part of the Commissioner’s work to investigate those cases.  </p>
<p>There are no costs associated with making a complaint to the Welsh Language Commissioner and all cases will be considered carefully. </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="flexibleblocks-block ">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row offset-xl-1">
                <div class="col-12 col-xl-11">
                    <div class="imagetext __animate __alt">
                            <div class="imagetext-image">
                                <img src="/media/3crmarcs/dsc0082-ansawddgwefan.jpg?center=0.3615729871231807,0.5309375713950143&amp;mode=crop&amp;width=650&amp;height=430&amp;rnd=132730869812900000" alt="Students sitting on stairs" data-object-fit="cover">
                            </div>
                        <div class="imagetext-body">
                            <div class="usercontent">
                                <p><strong>You have the right to: </strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/your-rights/make-a-complaint" title="Make a complaint">make a complaint</a> if there is a suspicion that an organisation is failing to comply with Welsh language standards;  </li>
<li><a href="/your-rights/make-a-complaint" title="Make a complaint">make a complaint</a> if there is a suspicion that an organisation is failing to comply with its Welsh language scheme;  </li>
<li>make an application to the Welsh Language Commissioner to rule on an allegation of interference with the <a href="/your-rights/freedom-to-use-welsh" title="Freedom to use Welsh">freedom to use the Welsh language</a>. </li>
</ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="flexibleblocks-block ">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row offset-xl-1">
                <div class="col-12 col-xl-11">
                    <div class="imagetext __animate __alt">
                            <div class="imagetext-image">
                                <img src="/media/5aihgap5/29062021comisiynyddygymraeg5791.jpg?anchor=center&amp;mode=crop&amp;width=650&amp;height=430&amp;rnd=132711596637530000" alt="Customer asking bank worker for help " data-object-fit="cover">
                            </div>
                        <div class="imagetext-body">
                            <div class="usercontent">
                                <p><strong>You have the <a href="/your-rights/freedom-to-use-welsh" title="Freedom to use Welsh">freedom to use the Welsh language</a> with other individuals in Wales.  </strong><strong>This means that no-one should: </strong></p>
<ul>
<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="5" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">prevent you from communicating in Welsh with another individual;  </li>
<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="5" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="4" data-aria-level="1">say that you will suffer in some way because you and another individual want to communicate in Welsh.  </li>
</ul>
<p>If this has happened to you, you can make an application asking the Commissioner to investigate what happened. </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

